SARDataComponentParams.title2:
Mining Module (Active):
Stabilizes the Deposit, reducing the Charge Rates of the deposit by 90% as well as reducing Shatter Damage by 90% if the deposit breaks. Mining laser must remain active on the deposit to maintain the effect. 
Duration: 20s
Uses: 5

Localization.Name: Greycat Industrial
Localization.Description: A trusted manufacturer of industrial tools since 2337, the company’s extensive line of industrial equipment and armor make it one of the most respected brand names around. Greycat has remained a UEE staple for centuries thanks to their streamlined-yet-inventive designs, exacting safety standards, and a diverse product line.

Localization.Name: Lifeline Module
Localization.Description:
Manufacturer: Greycat Industrial
Item Type: Mining Module (Active)

Laser Instability: -20
Resistance: -15%

Catastrophic Charge Rate: +60%

Duration: 15 seconds
Uses: 3

The Lifeline makes a miner's work easier by reducing laser instability and lessening resistance within a deposit. Yet, a higher catastrophic charge rate means the process must be carefully managed to avoid an accident.
